cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.DB 

This paper proposes a deep learning method for predictive modeling in healthcare using electronic health records (EHR) and medical ontologies. The method involves a graph-based attention mechanism and is evaluated on three healthcare prediction tasks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the method involves natural language processing of medical ontologies. Additionally, cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.DB (Databases) are also possible sub-categories as the paper deals with sensitive healthcare data and involves database management.
